<h2 class='page-intro'>CES Exhibitor News Conference Opportunities </h2>
<p class="intro">All media day events and CES news conferences, unless otherwise requested, will be included in the official CES Media Events Schedule and distributed on site at CES.</p>  

<h3 style="margin-bottom: -5px;"><img alt="CES Media Day" src="/CES/media/exhibitor-images/exhibitor-media-day_505x233.jpg" style="float: right; margin: auto 10px;" />CES Media Days</h3>

<p><strong>Media Day 1:</strong> Noon-2:45 PM, Jan. 7, 2018<br />
<strong>Media Day 2:</strong> 8 AM-5:45 PM, Jan. 8, 2018<br />
<strong>Location:</strong> Mandalay Bay</p>

<p>Make your major product or company news announcement exclusively to registered CES media and industry analysts with a Media Day news conference before the show floor opens.</p>

<p><strong>Selection in August 2017</strong><br />
You should receive your Media Day selection number in an email in early July.</p>

<p>If you do not receive a Media Day selection number, you can apply to be on the waitlist for any open slots, which will be filled on a first-come, first-served basis.</p>

<p><a href="/Exhibitor/Media-and-PR-Opportunities/News-Conferences/Media-Day-Wait-List.aspx"><img alt="" src="/CES/media/logos-and-icons/MDtimeslotbutton_1.jpg" /></a></p>
<div class="row"><div class="col-xs-60 col-sm-30 col-md-30"><h3 style="margin-bottom: -5px;"><img alt="Exhibitor Media Day Power Session" src="/CES/media/exhibitor-images/exhibitor-media-power-session_505x285.jpg" /><br />
CES Media Days Power Sessions</h3>

<p><strong>Date: </strong>Jan. 8, 2018<br />
<strong>Time: </strong>9 AM-12:45 PM<br />
<strong>Location:</strong> Mandalay Bay, Palm A Ballroom<br />
<strong>Cost: </strong>Free</p>

<p>Break news quickly and directly to CES media with a Media Day Power Session.</p>

<p>You will have 15 minutes for setup, 30 minutes for the event and 15 minutes for tear down. <a href="/CES/media/pdfs/CES-2017-Press-Day-Power-Session-Base-Package.pdf" target="_blank">See what&rsquo;s included in this space.</a> (PDF)</p>

<p>Sessions are available on a first-come, first-served basis.</p>

<p><a href="/Exhibitor/Media-and-PR-Opportunities/News-Conferences/Media-Day-Wait-List.aspx"><img alt="Sign up" src="/CES/media/logos-and-icons/sign-up-button.jpg" /></a></p>
</div><div class="col-xs-60 col-sm-30 col-md-30"><h3 style="margin-bottom: -5px;"><img alt="Show Day News Conference" src="/CES/media/exhibitor-images/show-day-news-conference_505x285.jpg" /><br />
Show Day News Conferences</h3>

<p><strong>Date: </strong>Jan. 9-10, 2018<br />
<strong>Time: </strong>Show floor hours<br />
<strong>Location: </strong>LVCC and The Venetian<br />
<strong>Cost:</strong> Free<br />
&nbsp;<br />
Hold news conference during the show in a CES-provided news conference room.&nbsp;</p>

<p><a href="/CES/media/pdfs/CES-2017-LVCC_Venetian_Press-Conference-Base-Packages.pdf" target="_blank">See what&rsquo;s included in the space</a>&nbsp;(PDF).&nbsp;Exhibitors are responsible for ordering and paying for additional services.</p>

<p>Sessions are available on a first-come, first-served basis.</p>

<p><a href="/Exhibitor/Media-and-PR-Opportunities/News-Conferences/News-Conference-Request-Form.aspx"><img alt="Sign up" src="/CES/media/logos-and-icons/sign-up-button.jpg" /></a></p>
</div><div class="clearfix visible-sm-block"></div><div class="clearfix visible-md-block visible-lg-block"></div></div><h3 style="margin-bottom: -5px;"><img alt="News Conference in Exhibit Space or Meeting Room" src="/CES/media/exhibitor-images/news-conference-meeting-room_505x233.jpg" style="float: right; margin: auto 10px;" />News Conferences in Your Exhibitor Booths or Meeting Rooms</h3>

<p><strong>Date: </strong>Jan. 9-12, 2017<br />
<strong>Time: </strong>Any*<br />
<strong>Location: </strong>CES-approved venue<br />
<strong>Cost: </strong>Free</p>

<p>Hold a news conference in your exhibit space or paid meeting space during the show. Notify us of your news conference for inclusion in promotional materials.</p>

<p><strong><u><a href="/Exhibitor/Opportunities/Media-and-PR-Opportunities/News-Conferences/News-Conference-Request-Form.aspx"><img alt="Notify Us" src="/CES/media/logos-and-icons/notify-us-button.JPG" /></a></u></strong></p>

<p><strong>Interested in booking a meeting room?</strong>&nbsp;Contact your&nbsp;<a href="/Exhibitor/Contact-a-Sales-Representative">sales representative</a>&nbsp;today.</p>

<p>*<em>Events held on the show floor before or after show hours require advanced security forms and hired security guards. If your form indicates that you&rsquo;d like to host your event before or after show hours, the CES PR team will send you the appropriate paperwork.</em></p>

<h3 style="margin-bottom: -5px;"><img alt="Warning" src="/getmedia/419fa5cf-5b6c-475a-bca0-fe296474094b/warning_285.aspx?width=175&amp;height=175" style="width: 175px; height: 175px; float: right; margin: auto 10px;" />The CES Stance on Outboarding</h3>

<p>Outboarding is any exhibit, demonstration, event or branded activation at a non-official CES venue, and it is a serious violation of CES policy and the International Association of Exhibitions and Events (IAEE) guidelines with consequences.</p>

<p>Please read the official&nbsp;<a href="/Exhibitor/CES-Outboarding-Policy.aspx" target="_blank">CES Stance on Outboarding</a>&nbsp;for more information.</p>

             
